# Converting to Grayscale

Grayscale conversion removes color information.

## Code:

```javascript
let src = cv.imread('canvasInput');
let dst = new cv.Mat();
cv.cvtColor(src, dst, cv.COLOR_RGBA2GRAY);
cv.imshow('canvasOutput', dst);
src.delete();
dst.delete();
```

