# Image Blurring

Blurring reduces noise and detail.

## Code:

```javascript
let src = cv.imread('canvasInput');
let dst = new cv.Mat();
let ksize = new cv.Size(5, 5);
cv.GaussianBlur(src, dst, ksize, 0);
cv.imshow('canvasOutput', dst);
src.delete();
dst.delete();
```

