# Edge Detection

Canny edge detection finds edges.

## Code:

```javascript
let src = cv.imread('canvasInput');
let dst = new cv.Mat();
cv.Canny(src, dst, 50, 100);
cv.imshow('canvasOutput', dst);
src.delete();
dst.delete();
```

