# Morphological Operations

Erosion and dilation modify shapes.

## Code:

```javascript
let src = cv.imread('canvasInput');
let dst = new cv.Mat();
let kernel = cv.Mat.ones(5, 5, cv.CV_8U);
cv.erode(src, dst, kernel);
cv.imshow('canvasOutput', dst);
src.delete();
dst.delete();
kernel.delete();
```

